thread.title: Jorge Chades
thread.title_full: Travel Insurance Center reviewed by Jorge Chades

author: Jorge Chades
title: Jorge Chades
text: Purchased a travel insurance policy for an 8 day S Africa Safari. The policy covered the same of a competitor at a lower rate. Met our representative Brandon Hughbanks at a recent travel show in DC. He's professional and very helpful clarifying and uncertainties.
